title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Cessna 172 Amphibian
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.0 of the Cessna 172 Amphibian. This aircraft is based on the Cessna 172 and has the ability to not only land on ground but also on water. 

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/15805/cessna-172-amphibian
